{"tid":1589174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"9月6日「反濫捕 抗威權」遮打集會帳目報告","createTime":"2019-09-23T07:15:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T10:31:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"917b28e7935f554b54edbaa90e7957edc9de3a56","tid":1589174,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:15:06.000Z","msg":"&quot;感謝23000名香港人出席9月6日的「反濫捕 抗威權」遮打集會。<br />\n<br />\n是次集會有乃你們的參與，及合共57名香港市民的響應，透過GoGetFunding網站，合共捐出了港幣$18,100。<br />\n<br />\n扣除眾籌網站及Paypal的手續費，最後我們共得 $16,528.65。我們得知有市民詢問其他的捐款方法，然而此平台的操作已是最快捷、公開、透明的眾籌方法，望各位見諒。<br />\n<br />\n是次集會開支︰<br />\n<br />\n租用音響設備︰$12,000<br />\n<br />\n運費︰165+190+201+246=802<br />\n<br />\n合共︰$12,802<br />\n<br />\n扣除開支後，共有餘款$3726.65，去除小數點後為$3726。並已按照約定，一半捐予 612人道支援基金 及 星火同盟 為手足支援，各$1863。<br />\n<br />\n所有單據可參考附件：<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1RarJ-ZZu0nq_hZdZ1SSXSU-1KHHlRGlF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fdrive%2Ffolders%2F1RarJ-ZZu0nq_hZdZ1SSXSU-1KHHlRGlF&d=%2B%2BEjZc3BRqGg7MXYxMXK66f05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=216b6b25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1RarJ-ZZu0nq_hZdZ1SSXSU-1KHHlRGlF</a><br />\n<br />\n在此再次感謝各位出錢出力的香港人。五大訴求，缺一不可！&quot;"},{"pid":"fff72d30e7c16338e5c289305571f303c634a3bd","tid":1589174,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"14835522272b8606c32d932d23e3026b2d5c7c9c","tid":1589174,"uid":230609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T07:16:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9dfa03282e69c43afe42a547614c2f745ffd61","tid":15891